Who's-Who : Developers

This page documents who is currently working on, or involved with each module hosted on netbeans.org. The data is read from the SourceCast member lists for each module, for example http://core.netbeans.org/servlets/ProjectMemberList, and updated daily. If you are a module owner, please keep the info on those pages up to date!

Module owner(s) are shown in bold face.
